<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="41" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="3.[136,1452,158,293]" pageId="3" pageNumber="41">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,506,158,184]" pageId="3" pageNumber="41">Distribution and Ecology:</emphasis>
— 
<taxonomicName box="[534,783,158,184]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Astragalus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="3" pageNumber="41" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="makuensis">
<emphasis box="[534,783,158,184]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="41">Astragalus makuensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is known only from the 
<typeStatus box="[1080,1128,159,185]" pageId="3" pageNumber="41">type</typeStatus>
locality, in W. Azarbayejan province (
<figureCitation box="[250,319,194,220]" captionStart="FIGURE 2" captionStartId="3.[136,229,1371,1393]" captionTargetBox="[177,1397,355,1334]" captionTargetId="figure-83@3.[151,1435,338,1354]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURE 2. Distribution map of Astragalus makuensis (●)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5145054" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5145054/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="41">Fig. 2</figureCitation>
). The new species grows on gravelly and rocky mountain slopes between 
<quantity box="[1151,1306,194,221]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.175" metricValueMax="2.2" metricValueMin="2.15" pageId="3" pageNumber="41" unit="m" value="2175.0" valueMax="2200.0" valueMin="2150.0">2150–2200 m</quantity>
elevation, in steppe vegetation of the Irano-Turanian phytogeographic region. It is part of the cushion forming vegetation 
<typeStatus box="[1353,1405,231,257]" pageId="3" pageNumber="41">type</typeStatus>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[136,1452,158,293]" box="[189,949,266,293]" pageId="3" pageNumber="41">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,323,266,292]" pageId="3" pageNumber="41">Phenology:</emphasis>
—Flowering June and early July; fruiting July or later
</paragraph>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5145054" ID-Zenodo-Dep="5145054" box="[136,707,1371,1393]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5145054/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="41" startId="3.[136,229,1371,1393]" targetBox="[177,1397,355,1334]" targetPageId="3">
<paragraph blockId="3.[136,707,1371,1393]" box="[136,707,1371,1393]" pageId="3" pageNumber="41">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[136,254,1371,1393]" pageId="3" pageNumber="41">FIGURE 2.</emphasis>
Distribution map of 
<taxonomicName box="[455,665,1371,1392]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Astragalus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="3" pageNumber="41" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="makuensis">
<emphasis box="[455,665,1371,1392]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="41">Astragalus makuensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(●).
</paragraph>
</caption>
<paragraph blockId="3.[136,1451,1440,1538]" pageId="3" pageNumber="41">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,400,1440,1466]" pageId="3" pageNumber="41">Taxonomic notes:</emphasis>
— 
<taxonomicName box="[428,674,1440,1466]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Astragalus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="3" pageNumber="41" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="makuensis">
<emphasis box="[428,674,1440,1466]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="41">Astragalus makuensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
clearly differs from its most closely related species, 
<taxonomicName authority="Fisch. &amp; C. A. Mey. (1853: 449)" authorityName="Fisch. &amp; C. A. Mey." authorityPageNumber="449" authorityYear="1853" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Astragalus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="3" pageNumber="41" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="hymenocystis">
<emphasis box="[1270,1451,1440,1466]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="41">A. hymenocystis</emphasis>
Fisch. &amp; C. A. Mey. (1853: 449)
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Maassoumi &amp; F. Ghahrem. (1999: 38)" authorityName="Maassoumi &amp; F. Ghahrem." authorityPageNumber="38" authorityYear="1999" box="[585,1268,1476,1502]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Astragalus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="3" pageNumber="41" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="pereshkhoranicus">
<emphasis box="[585,818,1476,1502]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="41">A. pereshkhoranicus</emphasis>
Maassoumi &amp; F.Ghahrem. (1999: 38)
</taxonomicName>
. The diagnostic characters distinguishing 
<taxonomicName box="[422,570,1512,1538]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Astragalus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="3" pageNumber="41" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="makuensis">
<emphasis box="[422,570,1512,1538]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="41">A. makuensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from its closely related taxa are summarized in Table 2.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
